00:03:20.490 --> 00:03:21.599
In the middle of the night,

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:22.639
a young woman,

00:03:23.080 --> 00:03:24.639
alone in Guangling Residence,

00:03:24.639 --> 00:03:26.879
runs into three suspicious men like us,

00:03:26.879 --> 00:03:28.199
yet you did not cry out.

00:03:28.840 --> 00:03:30.360
So what are you afraid of?

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.400
What is inside your bundle?

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:36.080
I…

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:48.790
There are night patrols
in the rear courtyard.

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:49.919
Let us step aside and talk.

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.560
The two in the water, come up as well.

00:03:52.680 --> 00:03:53.280
Stop flailing.

00:03:53.390 --> 00:03:54.439
The water is this shallow.

00:03:54.439 --> 00:03:55.639
Lan could not be in there.

00:03:55.639 --> 00:03:56.400
Come up first.

00:04:07.199 --> 00:04:07.680
Young lady.

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.879
The three of us are not bad people.

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:11.400
You do not need to be afraid.

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:12.560
As for who you are,

00:04:12.840 --> 00:04:13.759
we truly do not care.

00:04:15.100 --> 00:04:16.279
Please return the blade to me.

00:04:18.319 --> 00:04:19.839
I know you are not villains.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:22.980
With so much gold and treasure in this residence,
you did not steal any of it.

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:24.959
Yet you came
for this battered little blade.

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:27.639
You must have your reasons.

00:04:29.090 --> 00:04:30.290
But that is none of my concern.

00:04:30.300 --> 00:04:32.050
As long as you help me
with one small favor,

00:04:32.120 --> 00:04:34.360
I promise I will return the blade to you,

00:04:34.450 --> 00:04:35.240
and keep this quiet.

00:04:36.279 --> 00:04:37.920
How do you want us to help you?

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:41.040
Since I was young,

00:04:42.399 --> 00:04:44.160
I have served
in this residence as a maid.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:47.020
