one last time.

00:04:54.439 --> 00:04:55.000
Enough.

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:57.660
You want us to help you escape
from Guangling Residence, right?

00:04:57.920 --> 00:04:59.040
Not just the residence.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.160
I need to leave Lin'an City.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:01.399
In Lin'an City,

00:05:01.400 --> 00:05:02.970
Guangling Residence holds immense power.

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:05.759
Nearly all the city guards
are in their pocket.

00:05:05.879 --> 00:05:07.920
Even if someone escapes the residence,

00:05:08.079 --> 00:05:09.170
they cannot escape the city.

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:10.160
That is why

00:05:10.759 --> 00:05:11.800
I need your help.

00:05:13.959 --> 00:05:14.879
Young lady,

00:05:15.279 --> 00:05:18.600
