00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:20.519
Follow me.

00:06:24.260 --> 00:06:25.079
Let us get out first.

00:06:25.079 --> 00:06:25.990
You think we will lose our way?

00:06:26.199 --> 00:06:27.120
We will not.

00:06:30.279 --> 00:06:31.160
Hurry.

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:34.279
You really are amazing.

00:06:34.280 --> 00:06:35.660
There is not a single guard around.

00:06:35.839 --> 00:06:37.879
You were just lucky to run into me.

00:06:37.880 --> 00:06:39.420
We take the side path to the back gate.

00:06:39.439 --> 00:06:41.519
It is the fastest and safest route.

00:06:45.520 --> 00:06:46.319
What are you doing?

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:47.420
