00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.439
Who is Jin?

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.120
That's none of your business.

00:07:31.130 --> 00:07:32.150
You think I didn't notice?

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:33.820
The one who shouted
about the fire just now.

00:07:33.839 --> 00:07:35.399
You must have planned this
for a long time.

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:36.420
Weren't you afraid she'd suffer for it?

00:07:36.439 --> 00:07:36.839
I...

00:07:38.279 --> 00:07:39.720
