could make its scent fade,

00:10:33.799 --> 00:10:35.120
then it would be a cheap trinket.

00:10:35.559 --> 00:10:37.879
How could I ever present
such a thing to a Princess?

00:10:40.399 --> 00:10:41.200
Old Madam.

00:10:43.039 --> 00:10:46.159
When you gave me that sachet,
you had already foreseen today, hadn't you?

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:49.519
