00:13:29.559 --> 00:13:30.559
Give me a break.

00:13:30.559 --> 00:13:32.600
Be glad you did not get it
all over your own face.

00:13:34.679 --> 00:13:36.440
The Kun Blade is still
with the Princess.

00:13:36.759 --> 00:13:37.480
What do we do now?

00:13:37.799 --> 00:13:40.360
I knew from the start
she was not simple.

00:13:40.960 --> 00:13:42.879
A servant girl
would never have such a temper.

00:13:42.880 --> 00:13:44.710
And someone even helped
draw the guards away for her.

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:46.080
There was nothing else we could do.

00:13:46.080 --> 00:13:48.490
The situation was too urgent,
we had no choice but to agree.

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:50.120
So what now?

00:13:50.320 --> 00:13:51.240
Let us lie low for now.

00:14:30.039 --> 00:14:30.840
Old Madam.

00:14:38.320 --> 00:14:39.080
My Lord.

00:14:40.039 --> 00:14:41.799
