00:14:42.639 --> 00:14:44.000
I, a mere woman,

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:47.960
have carried the burdens
of the entire residence on my own.

00:14:48.360 --> 00:14:51.559
Now at last, we have been granted
an auspicious match.

00:14:52.519 --> 00:14:53.559
Yan Rong

00:14:54.320 --> 00:14:55.799
has brought honor to the family name.

00:14:56.440 --> 00:14:58.519
